The '''Sauvax language''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Sauvax]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Leritor/Legends|Leritor]]. Their [[Mouth/Legends|mouths]] were advanced enough to pronounce most of the needed sounds for usual languages such as [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].<ref name="u">''[[Ultimate Alien Anthology]]''</ref>

Due to the infrequent contact with the [[galactic community]], some Sauvax were fluent in both Sauvax language and Basic, although they were only literate in their own language.<ref name="u" />

